OL,7,FInflation-hit shoppers cut spending by
OL,8,Frecord amounts last month, dashing
OL,9,Fhopes of a Christmas boost for the
OL,10,Fcountry's flagging retail sector.
OL,12,FA 1 per cent drop in sales volumes
OL,13,Fmirrored November's 0.5 per cent fall,
OL,14,Fwhen Black Friday failed to produce a
OL,15,Fboost in sales, according to the Office
OL,16,Ffor National Statistics (ONS).
OL,18,FDecember's volumes were down by 5.8 per
OL,19,Fcent compared with December 2021, the
OL,20,Fbiggest fall for that month in records
OL,21,Fgoing back to 1997.
